 is H. Everts (Philadelphia: Louis H. Everts\, 1881)\, 1:63.\n4 Thomas Armi
 tage\, The History of the Baptists (1890\; reprint ed.\, Watertown. Wis.: 
 Maranatha Baptist Press\, 1976)\, 2:853. \n5 Jesse L. Boyd\, A History of 
 the Baptists in America Prior to 1845 (New York: American Press\, 1957)\, 
 hal. 86.\n6 Benedict\, hal. 396.\n
