 obert A. Baker\, The Southern Baptist Convention and Its People\, 1607-197
 2 (Nashville: Broadman Press\, 1974)\, hal. 302.\n4 Cox\, 2:923.\n5 L. Rus
 s Bush and Tom J. Nettles\, Baptists and the Bible (Chicago: Moody Press\,
  1980)\, hal. 227.\n
