 rey Bonner\, Some Baptist Hymnists from the Seventeenth Century to Modern 
 Times (London: Carey Kingsgate Press\, 1937)\, hal. 123.\n4 Kathleen Blanc
 hard\, Stories of Beautiful Hymns (Grand Rapids: Zondervan Publishing Hous
 e\, 1952)\, hal. 54.\n5 Ibid.\, hal. 55. \n\n
