 al Story of Texas Baptists (Dallas: Baptist General Convention of Texas\, 
 1936)\, hal. 22.\n3 Robert\, A. Baker\, The Blossoming Desert (Waco\, Tex.
 : Word Books\, 1970)\, hal. 28-29.\n4 Elliott\, hal. 10.\n
